Build a transformer-based language model from scratch with the following specifications:

## Model Architecture
- **Style:** GPT (autoregressive, decoder-only)
- **Target size:** 100–200M parameters
- **Layers:** 12 transformer blocks
- **Hidden dimensions:** 768
- **Attention heads:** 12 (multi-head attention)

## Components
- Embedding layers (token + positional)
- Multi-head self-attention
- Feed-forward layers
- Layer normalization

## Training Configuration
- **Optimizer:** Adam
- **Objective:** Next-token prediction
- **Mixed precision:** Enabled
- **Gradient checkpointing:** Enabled

## Output
- Model summary
- Total parameter count
